Cosine Kernels: 25X

rm(list=ls())
library(data.table)
library(Matrix)

simpath = "/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/kdc/experiment/simulation/v3/data/rds/"
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/freq_func.R")
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/simple_plot.R")

cos_trans <- function(x,lkernel=5){
    l   <- quantile(x,probs=seq(0.1,1,by=0.1))
    out <- cos(2*pi*x/l[lkernel])
    return(out)
}

iblock = 25
load(paste0(simpath,"/sim_data_CN24_E1_",iblock,"X_ONL_zero5_sigzero5_rpt5.rds"))

raw_loc     <- as.matrix(location[,1:2])
cor_list <- cov_list <- list()
for(iker in 1:10){
    trans_loc   <- apply(raw_loc,2,cos_trans,lkernel=iker)
    scale_trans_loc     <- apply(trans_loc,2,scale)
    order_loc       <- scale_trans_loc[order(scale_trans_loc[,1],scale_trans_loc[,2]),]
    kmat        <- order_loc %*% solve(t(order_loc) %*% order_loc) %*% t(order_loc)
    a           <- cov2cor(kmat)
    cor_list[[iker]] <- ht_map_K_uniform(a,lgd=F,main=paste0("Cosine_Correlation",iker))
    cov_list[[iker]] <- ht_map_K_uniform(kmat,lgd=F,main=paste0("Cosine_Covariance",iker))
    rm(a,kmat,trans_loc,scale_trans_loc,order_loc)
}

library(ggpubr)
fig1 <- ggarrange(cor_list[[1]],cor_list[[2]],
                cor_list[[3]],cor_list[[4]],
                cor_list[[5]],cor_list[[6]],
                cor_list[[7]],cor_list[[8]],
                cor_list[[9]],cor_list[[10]],
                ncol = 5, nrow = 2)

fig2 <- ggarrange(cov_list[[1]],cov_list[[2]],
                cov_list[[3]],cov_list[[4]],
                cov_list[[5]],cov_list[[6]],
                cov_list[[7]],cov_list[[8]],
                cov_list[[9]],cov_list[[10]],
                ncol = 5, nrow = 2)

Gaussian Kernels: 25X

rm(list=ls())
library(data.table)
library(Matrix)

simpath = "/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/kdc/experiment/simulation/v3/data/rds/"
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/freq_func.R")
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/simple_plot.R")


gaus_trans <- function(x,lkernel=5){
    l   <- quantile(x,probs=seq(0.1,1,by=0.1))
    out <- exp(-x^2/(2*l[lkernel]^2))
    return(out)
}

iblock = 25
load(paste0(simpath,"/sim_data_CN24_E1_",iblock,"X_ONL_zero5_sigzero5_rpt5.rds"))

raw_loc     <- as.matrix(location[,1:2])
cor_list <- cov_list <- list()
for(iker in 1:10){
    trans_loc   <- apply(raw_loc,2,gaus_trans,lkernel=iker)
    scale_trans_loc     <- apply(trans_loc,2,scale)
    order_loc       <- scale_trans_loc[order(scale_trans_loc[,1],scale_trans_loc[,2]),]
    kmat        <-  order_loc %*% solve(t(order_loc) %*% order_loc) %*% t(order_loc)
    a           <- cov2cor(kmat)
    cor_list[[iker]] <- ht_map_K_uniform(a,lgd=F,main=paste0("Gaussian_Correlation",iker))
    cov_list[[iker]] <- ht_map_K_uniform(kmat,lgd=F,main=paste0("Gaussian_Covariance",iker))
    rm(a,kmat,trans_loc,scale_trans_loc,order_loc)
}

library(ggpubr)
fig3 <- ggarrange(cor_list[[1]],cor_list[[2]],
                cor_list[[3]],cor_list[[4]],
                cor_list[[5]],cor_list[[6]],
                cor_list[[7]],cor_list[[8]],
                cor_list[[9]],cor_list[[10]],
                ncol = 5, nrow = 2)

fig4 <- ggarrange(cov_list[[1]],cov_list[[2]],
                cov_list[[3]],cov_list[[4]],
                cov_list[[5]],cov_list[[6]],
                cov_list[[7]],cov_list[[8]],
                cov_list[[9]],cov_list[[10]],
                ncol = 5, nrow = 2)
